These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, lemonade, mirinda, water
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, animation, crime, time-travel
1. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching crime movies##5
2. the person drinking lemonade is not the person watching fantasy movies##6
3. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching time-travel movies##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
5. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
6. the person watching fantasy movies is not the person drinking mirinda##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | lemonade   | water    | juice    | mirinda |
| Sport      | time-travel | fantasy | crime | animation |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, milk, mirinda, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, musical, adventure, western
1. the person watching crime movies is on the far right##1
2. the person drinking milk is somewhere to the left of the person drinking mirinda##5
3. the person watching western movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking sprite##5
4. the person drinking milk is not the person watching musical movies##6
5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
7. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
8. the person drinking mirinda is somewhere to the left of the person drinking iced-tea##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | milk  | mirinda    | iced-tea | sprite    |
| Food       | western | musical | adventure  | crime |

