.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
City: new-york, boston, prague, paris
1. the person drinking water is not the person traveling to new-york##6
2. the person traveling to boston is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the person traveling to prague is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the person traveling to boston is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to paris##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | prague | paris | boston | new-york  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-4::.
City: marseilles, san-francisco, nizza, hannover
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, subway, train, trike
1. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
2. the person traveling to san-francisco is somewhere to the left of the person driving the quad-bike##5
3. the person driving the trike is not the person traveling to san-francisco##6
4. the person driving the trike is somewhere to the right of the person driving the quad-bike##5
5. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
6. the person traveling to hannover is somewhere to the left of the person driving the trike##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |    4     |
| Pet         | san-francisco | nizza | hannover     | marseilles |
| Transport   | subway     | train    | quad-bike | trike    |

