.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: brown, turquise, lavender, emerald
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, snowmobile
1. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
2. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person who likes emerald is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person who likes turquise is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person driving the bike is not the person who likes brown##6
6. the person who likes lavender is on the left of the person who likes turquise##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | brown        | emerald | lavender | turquise |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | boat     | car   |

