.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
4 different games are played: bridge, billiard, go, chess
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing chess is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the person playing go is the person playing go##1
6. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the person playing go is somewhere to the left of the person playing bridge##5
8. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the person playing billiard is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | billiard | go    | bridge  | chess   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

