2. the person who's hobby is photography is not the person watching spy movies##6
3. the person watching documentary movies is the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3
5. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
6. the person watching spy movies is the person who's hobby is camping##1
7. the person watching zombie movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is camping##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |      3      |      4      |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | spy     | time-travel | documentary |
| Music-Genre   | photography | camping | hiking      | singing         |

