.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, mystery, sports, family
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the person watching zombie movies##6
2. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person watching family movies is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the person watching sports movies is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the person watching mystery movies##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the person watching sports movies is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | sports | zombie        | family  | mystery     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

