.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-11::.
City: liverpool, rome, venice, paris
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: disco, electronic, indie, pop
1. the person traveling to liverpool is on the left or right of the person traveling to paris##3
2. the fan electronic is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to liverpool##5
3. the fan indie is not the person traveling to venice##6
4. the person traveling to rome is between the fan pop and the person traveling to venice##2
5. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
6. the fan electronic is between the fan disco and the person traveling to liverpool##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |   3   |     4     |
| Hobby         | venice | rome    | liverpool | paris |
| Music-Genre   | disco         | electronic | pop   | indie     |

