.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-12::.
House: victorian, ranch-style, gothic-revival, craftsman
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, bus, snowmobile, trike
1. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
2. the craftsman house is not the person driving the bike##6
3. the person driving the bus is the craftsman house##1
4. the person driving the bus is on the right of the ranch-style house##1
5. the person driving the snowmobile is not the craftsman house##6
6. the ranch-style house is not the person driving the bike##6
7. the gothic-revival house is somewhere to the left of the ranch-style house##5
8. the victorian house is on the left of the gothic-revival house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |    2     |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | victorian  | gothic-revival | ranch-style | craftsman |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike     | trike     | bus    |

