3. the person eating asparagus is the person who likes azure##1
4. the person eating lettuce is somewhere to the right of the person who likes brown##5
5. the person eating asparagus is between the person eating banana and the person who likes coral##2
6. the person eating banana is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
