The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, biathlon, weightlifting, skiing
1. the person who's sport is skiing is on the left or right of the person drinking iced-tea##3
2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the person who's sport is biathlon##3
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the person who's sport is tennis is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is biathlon##5
6. the person who's sport is biathlon is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | skiing  | biathlon   | weightlifting | tennis |

 